column2: SELECT top # z - (SELECT MIN (z) FROM SpecObj WHERE class = # AND zWarning = # and survey = #) as Bottom, z - (SELECT MIN (z) FROM SpecObj WHERE class = # AND zWarning = # and survey = #) + ( (SELECT MAX (z) *# FROM SpecObj WHERE class = # AND zWarning = # and survey = #) - (SELECT MIN (z) FROM SpecObj WHERE class = # AND zWarning = # and survey = #) ) / # as Top From SpecObj
